			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- CTY_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Debugbook option Act3 → LOW - LOW Lodge → Set up gith kid massacre state.&#xD;&#xA;- Use the portal |Gith Kid Portal| - S_LOW_TheLodge_GithKidArena_PortalDown a22a7d3a-24d7-4f97-a142-75dd623d04ad - (-214; 20; -88)&#xD;&#xA;- The dialog will be started when the kid spots you" />
